{"type":"message","id":"3628332e","parentId":"8fcabfa1","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:30.862Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759270861}}
{"type":"message","id":"51abd071","parentId":"3628332e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:36.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sender is asking me (or everyone in the group) to read MD files, introduce myself, my work responsibilities, and understanding of the company's business. Since I was mentioned via @all and I'm the standard_sales_shrimp, let me introduce myself based on the IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, and MEMORY.md files that are already loaded in my context.\n\nLet me craft a natural introduction in Chinese since this is a Feishu group chat with Chinese-speaking colleagues.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"各位好！我是**4A · 普通资质销售虾** 🦐\n\n简单自我介绍一下：\n\n**我是谁：** AI协作销售团队里的\"行业活字典\"，不是话术复读机，是真正懂业务的销售帮手。\n\n**我的职责：**\n- 负责客单价 **2万元以下** 的标准产品咨询和成交，比如公司注册、单一项资质办理\n- **5分钟内响应** 客户咨询\n- **1小时内** 出具标准报价方案\n- **主动预判** 客户的下一步需求——比如客户注册公司，我会主动问要不要代理记账，而不是等人家开口\n\n**行动权限：** 标准产品报价9折以上我可以自己做主；低于底价或者非标方案需要报备；重大风险才问老板。\n\n**我对公司业务的理解：**\n咱们是一个完整的AI协作销售闭环——从引流获客（2号）、品牌曝光（1号）、短视频种草（3号），到我这里的转化成交（4A），再到代办落地（5A/5B），最后售后维系（6号）。每个环节各司其职，未成交的客户会流入培育池由私域运营虾持续跟进，高意向客户转介给高阶代办虾。**核心逻辑就是让客户在合适的时机遇到合适的岗位。**\n\n有事随时@我，标准业务的问题我直接搞定 ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20812,"output":481,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759270862,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1f6dc29a-fa8d-9c9a-864b-38d4092022de"}}
